{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847601787,"sessionID":"ses_2873ed6d6ffebx07opRS5b8lQ3","part":{"id":"prt_d78c3f64a001c3Yty1NPdj57J7","messageID":"msg_d78c31e6f001D62A0iM3GpQZRm","sessionID":"ses_2873ed6d6ffebx07opRS5b8lQ3","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a820d80a7204464599dd979432442ca2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n**AR**: AR-008  \n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Implement periodic garbage collection for sandbox resources based on idle timeout and TTL expiry.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     WorkloadManager                         │\n│                                                              │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │              GarbageCollector                        │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐     │  │\n│  │  │ gcLoop()   │  │ tick()     │  │ deleteSandbox() │  │  │\n│  │  │ (ticker)   │  │ (timeout)  │  │ (K8s API + Store) │ │\n│  │  └────────────┘  └────────────┘  └────────────┘     │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n         │                        │\n         │                        │\n         ▼                        ▼\n┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐\n│  Kubernetes API  │  │     Redis Store  │\n│  (Sandbox CRDs)  │  │  (Session Data)  │\n└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Cleanup Triggers\n\n1. **Idle Timeout**: Sandboxes with `LastActivityAt < now - DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` (15 minutes)\n2. **TTL Expiry**: Sandboxes with `ExpiresAt < now`\n3. **Manual Deletion**: Explicit session deletion via API\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### GarbageCollector\n\n**File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go`\n\n```go\ntype GarbageCollector struct {\n\tdynamicClient dynamic.Interface  // Kubernetes dynamic client for CRD operations\n\tstoreClient   store.Store        // Redis store for session data\n\tinterval      time.Duration      // GC run interval (default: 15s)\n\tctx           context.Context    // Context for cancellation\n\tcancel        context.CancelFunc // Cancel function for graceful shutdown\n}\n```\n\n### Cleanup Reasons\n\n**File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go`\n\n```go\ntype SandboxCleanupReason string\n\nconst (\n\tCleanupReasonManual      SandboxCleanupReason = \"manual\"\n\tCleanupReasonIdleTimeout SandboxCleanupReason = \"idle_timeout\"\n\tCleanupReasonExpired     SandboxCleanupReason = \"expired\"\n)\n```\n\n### Audit Entry\n\n```go\ntype CleanupAuditEntry struct {\n\tSessionID    string               `json:\"sessionId\"`\n\tSandboxID    string               `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n\tNamespace    string               `json:\"namespace\"`\n\tReason       SandboxCleanupReason `json:\"reason\"`\n\tDeletedAt    time.Time            `json:\"deletedAt\"`\n\tSuccess      bool                 `json:\"success\"`\n\tErrorMessage string               `json:\"errorMessage,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Kubernetes CRD Resources\n\nThe GarbageCollector operates on two CRD types:\n\n| GVR | Group | Version | Resource |\n|-----|-------|---------|----------|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes` | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `sandboxes` |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims` | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `sandboxclaims` |\n\n### Store Interface\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n\t// ListExpiredSandboxes returns sandboxes with ExpiresAt < before\n\tListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n\t\n\t// ListInactiveSandboxes returns sandboxes with LastActivityAt < before\n\tListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n\t\n\t// DeleteSandboxBySessionID removes session data from Redis\n\tDeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n}\n```\n\n### SandboxInfo (from Store)\n\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n\tSessionID           string    `json:\"sessionId\"`\n\tSandboxID           string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n\tSandboxNamespace    string    `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n\tKind                string    `json:\"kind\"` // \"Sandbox\" or \"SandboxClaim\"\n\tExpiresAt           time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n\tLastActivityAt      time.Time `json:\"lastActivityAt\"`\n}\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Error Scenarios\n\n| Scenario | Handling |\n|----------|----------|\n| Store query fails | Log error, continue to next query |\n| K8s API delete fails (NotFound) | Treat as success, delete from store |\n| K8s API delete fails (other) | Log error, audit as failure, continue |\n| Store delete fails | Log warning (not critical) |\n| Context timeout | Cancel current tick, retry next interval |\n\n### Error Logging\n\nAll errors are logged with structured fields:\n- Session ID\n- Sandbox ID\n- Namespace\n- Reason\n- Error message\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n**File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go`\n\n```go\npackage workloadmanager_test\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"testing\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2\"\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\tdynamicfake \"k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n)\n\nvar _ = Describe(\"GarbageCollector\", func() {\n\tvar (\n\t\tfakeDynamicClient *dynamicfake.FakeDynamicClient\n\t\tfakeStore         *FakeStore\n\t\tgc                *workloadmanager.GarbageCollector\n\t\tctx               context.Context\n\t)\n\n\tBeforeEach(func() {\n\t\tscheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n\t\tfakeDynamicClient = dynamicfake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\t\tfakeStore = NewFakeStore()\n\t\tgc = workloadmanager.NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, fakeStore, 100*time.Millisecond)\n\t\tctx = context.Background()\n\t})\n\n\tAfterEach(func() {\n\t\tgc.Stop()\n\t})\n\n\tContext(\"Cleanup of idle sandboxes\", func() {\n\t\tIt(\"should delete sandboxes idle for more than timeout\", func() {\n\t\t\tsandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n\t\t\t\tSessionID:        \"test-session\",\n\t\t\t\tSandboxID:        \"test-sandbox\",\n\t\t\t\tSandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n\t\t\t\tKind:             \"Sandbox\",\n\t\t\t\tExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(1 * time.Hour),\n\t\t\t\tLastActivityAt:   time.Now().Add(-20 * time.Minute),\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tfakeStore.AddSandbox(sandbox)\n\n\t\t\tgc.Start()\n\t\t\ttime.Sleep(200 * time.Millisecond)\n\n\t\t\tEventually(func() bool {\n\t\t\t\treturn fakeStore.IsDeleted(\"test-session\")\n\t\t\t}).Should(BeTrue())\n\t\t})\n\t})\n\n\tContext(\"Cleanup of expired sandboxes\", func() {\n\t\tIt(\"should delete sandboxes past their TTL\", func() {\n\t\t\tsandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n\t\t\t\tSessionID:        \"test-session\",\n\t\t\t\tSandboxID:        \"test-sandbox\",\n\t\t\t\tSandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n\t\t\t\tKind:             \"Sandbox\",\n\t\t\t\tExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(-1 * time.Hour),\n\t\t\t\tLastActivityAt:   time.Now(),\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tfakeStore.AddSandbox(sandbox)\n\n\t\t\tgc.Start()\n\t\t\ttime.Sleep(200 * time.Millisecond)\n\n\t\t\tEventually(func() bool {\n\t\t\t\treturn fakeStore.IsDeleted(\"test-session\")\n\t\t\t}).Should(BeTrue())\n\t\t})\n\t})\n\n\tContext(\"Error handling\", func() {\n\t\tIt(\"should continue on store errors\", func() {\n\t\t\tfakeStore.FailOnQuery = true\n\n\t\t\tgc.Start()\n\t\t\ttime.Sleep(200 * time.Millisecond)\n\n\t\t\tExpect(fakeStore.QueryCount).To(BeNumerically(\">\", 0))\n\t\t})\n\t})\n})\n```\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n**File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_gc_test.go`\n\n```go\npackage workloadmanager_test\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"testing\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2\"\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n\t\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/envtest\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n)\n\nvar _ = Describe(\"GarbageCollector Integration\", func() {\n\tvar (\n\t\tenvTest *envtest.Environment\n\t\tgc      *workloadmanager.GarbageCollector\n\t)\n\n\tBeforeSuite(func() {\n\t\tenvTest = &envtest.Environment{\n\t\t\tCRDDirectoryPaths: []string{\"../../manifests/charts/base/crds\"},\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tcfg, err := envTest.Start()\n\t\tExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\n\t\tdynamicClient, err := dynamic.NewForConfig(cfg)\n\t\tExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\n\t\tstore, err := store.NewRedisStore(...)\n\t\tExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\n\t\tgc = workloadmanager.NewGarbageCollector(dynamicClient, store, 15*time.Second)\n\t\tgc.Start()\n\t})\n\n\tAfterSuite(func() {\n\t\tgc.Stop()\n\t\terr := envTest.Stop()\n\t\tExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\t})\n\n\tIt(\"should cleanup real sandbox resources\", func(ctx SpecContext) {\n\t\tsessionID := \"integration-test-session\"\n\t\t\n\t\terr := store.CreateSession(ctx, sessionID, &store.SessionMetadata{\n\t\t\tExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(-1 * time.Hour),\n\t\t\tLastActivity: time.Now(),\n\t\t}, 0)\n\t\tExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\n\t\tEventually(func() bool {\n\t\t\t_, err := store.GetSession(ctx, sessionID)\n\t\t\treturn err != nil\n\t\t}, 30*time.Second, time.Second).Should(BeTrue())\n\t}, SpecTimeout(60*time.Second))\n})\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n### Default Constants\n\n**File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`\n\n```go\nconst (\n\tDefaultSandboxTTL         = 8 * time.Hour\n\tDefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n\tGCInterval                = 15 * time.Second\n\tGCSingleTickTimeout       = 2 * time.Minute\n\tDeleteTimeout             = 30 * time.Second\n\tBatchSize                 = 16\n)\n```\n\n### Configuration Options\n\n| Option | Type | Default | Description |\n|--------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `Session.DefaultTimeout` | `time.Duration` | `15m` | Idle timeout for cleanup |\n| `Session.MaxDuration` | `time.Duration` | `8h` | Maximum session TTL |\n| `Session.CleanupInterval` | `time.Duration` | `15s` | GC run interval |\n\n## Metrics\n\n### Prometheus Metrics\n\n```go\nconst (\n\tmetricGCRunsTotal           = \"workloadmanager_gc_runs_total\"\n\tmetricGCDeletedSandboxes    = \"workloadmanager_gc_deleted_sandboxes_total\"\n\tmetricGCDeletionFailures    = \"workloadmanager_gc_deletion_failures_total\"\n\tmetricGCTickDuration        = \"workloadmanager_gc_tick_duration_seconds\"\n)\n\nvar (\n\tgcRunsTotal = prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n\t\tprometheus.CounterOpts{\n\t\t\tName: metricGCRunsTotal,\n\t\t\tHelp: \"Total number of GC runs\",\n\t\t},\n\t\t[]string{\"reason\"},\n\t)\n\n\tgcDeletedSandboxes = prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n\t\tprometheus.CounterOpts{\n\t\t\tName: metricGCDeletedSandboxes,\n\t\t\tHelp: \"Total number of sandboxes deleted by GC\",\n\t\t},\n\t\t[]string{\"reason\", \"kind\"},\n\t)\n\n\tgcTickDuration = prometheus.NewHistogramVec(\n\t\tprometheus.HistogramOpts{\n\t\t\tName:    metricGCTickDuration,\n\t\t\tHelp:    \"GC tick duration in seconds\",\n\t\t\tBuckets: prometheus.DefBuckets,\n\t\t},\n\t\t[]string{\"reason\"},\n\t)\n)\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### Go Module Dependencies\n\n```go\nrequire (\n\tk8s.io/client-go v0.32.1  // dynamic.Interface for CRD operations\n\tgo-redis/v9 v9.7.0        // store.Store interface\n\tk8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1  // structured logging\n)\n```\n\n### Kubernetes RBAC\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager-gc\nrules:\n- apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n  resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n  verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"delete\"]\n- apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n  resources: [\"sandboxclaims\"]\n  verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"delete\"]\n```\n\n## Lifecycle Management\n\n### Startup\n\n```go\n// In server.go\nfunc (s *Server) Start() error {\n\t// ... other initialization\n\n\t// Start garbage collector\n\ts.garbageCollector = NewGarbageCollector(\n\t\ts.k8sClient.DynamicClient,\n\t\ts.store,\n\t\ts.config.Session.CleanupInterval,\n\t)\n\ts.garbageCollector.Start()\n\n\t// Start HTTP server\n\t// ...\n}\n```\n\n### Shutdown\n\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) Stop() error {\n\ts.cancel()\n\n\t// Stop garbage collector\n\tif s.garbageCollector != nil {\n\t\ts.garbageCollector.Stop()\n\t}\n\n\t// Wait for goroutines\n\ts.wg.Wait()\n\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n1. **RBAC Enforcement**: GC service account requires minimal permissions (delete only on sandbox resources)\n2. **Namespace Isolation**: GC respects sandbox namespace boundaries\n3. **Audit Logging**: All deletions are logged with session ID, sandbox ID, and reason\n4. **Error Handling**: Partial failures don't affect other sandboxes\n\n## Performance Characteristics\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| GC Interval | 15 seconds |\n| Batch Size | 16 sandboxes per tick |\n| Single Tick Timeout | 2 minutes |\n| Delete Timeout | 30 seconds per sandbox |\n| Storage Overhead | O(n) where n = number of sessions |\n| API Load | ~1-2 req/s per 1000 active sessions |","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design-gc.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go\">\nERROR [63:7] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [106:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [173:2] declared and not used: logger\nERROR [242:5] undefined: podSpecsEqual\nERROR [267:29] undefined: convertEnvVars\nERROR [274:25] undefined: convertResources\nERROR [326:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/controller.go\">\nERROR [57:3] unknown field MetricsBindAddress in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [58:3] unknown field Port in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [62:3] unknown field SyncPeriod in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [88:17] undefined: AgentRuntimeReconciler\nERROR [98:15] cannot use ctrl.Options{…} (value of struct type controllerruntime.Options) as controller.TypedOptions[reconcile.Request] value in argument to ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}).WithEventFilter(&ResourceGenerationChangedPredicate{}).WithOptions\nERROR [98:28] unknown field MaxConcurrentReconciles in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [118:15] cannot use ctrl.Options{…} (value of struct type controllerruntime.Options) as controller.TypedOptions[reconcile.Request] value in argument to ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}).WithEventFilter(&ResourceGenerationChangedPredicate{}).WithOptions\nERROR [118:28] unknown field MaxConcurrentReconciles in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":62,"character":6},"end":{"line":62,"character":27}},"severity":1,"code":"UndeclaredName","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/internal/typesinternal#UndeclaredName"},"source":"compiler","message":"undefined: statusConditionsEqual"},{"ran